metadata.name: Altruistic Angels of our Hearts
metadata.description:
The year is 5783, the presentation of being drawn into greater intimacy.

Do you hear the call?  Do you connect the dots?  Do you sense the stars?  Do you feel the angels? 

Become aware of the classified effortless actions– the invisible mystery of our world – 

Communicate and identify what we are talking about – emerge from the mystery –

We are cultivating a practice and being in the form, simultaneously living in the mystery of our hearts. The mystery itself is the door for all being – let's enjoy the unknown, just be and stay open for surprises and the fruitfulness of the secret to unfold –

Some of our desires are how we think the universe should be instead of observing the potential to emerge and meet in our hearts –

-	Jai be the heart-to-heart - 
❤
